Code.Terraform:
```hcl
resource "azurerm_backup_policy_vm" "<example_resource_name>" {
  name                = "<example_resource_name>"
  resource_group_name = "<example_resource_id>"
  recovery_vault_name = "<example_resource_name>"

  backup {
    frequency = "Daily"
    time      = "23:00"
  }

  retention_daily {
    count = 30  # Critical: retains daily backups for 30 days
  }
}
```
